type(scope): short summary

# Types:
# feat, fix, refactor, style, test, chore, docs
#
# Examples:
# feat(cart): persist cart to localStorage
# refactor(products): migrate list to typed service layer
# chore(config): add eslint flat config
#
# Body:
# Explain what changed and why.
# Keep lines concise and focused on reviewer context.
#
# Footer:
# Optional references, follow-ups, or breaking changes.
